        "input": {
          "op": "contains_miss",
          "target": 99
        },
        "expected": false
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "op": "remove",
          "target": 5
        },
        "expected": "removed"
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "op": "remove_missing"
        },
        "expected": "ValueError"
      }
    ],
    "hints": [
      "💡 `bisect_left` O(log n) index bul",
      "💡 `insort` otomatik insert at correct position",
      "💡 `list.pop(idx)` ile remove"
    ],
    "explanation": "SortedList: add → insort(data, value), remove → bisect_left + pop, contains → idx >= 0 and idx < len and data[idx]==value. Average O(n) insert ama sorted maintain eder, search O(log n).",
