  {
    "id": 1118,
    "title": "Coverage-Driven Test Suite",
    "category": "testing",
    "level": "intermediate",
    "description": "Bir fonksiyonun tum branch'lerini kapsayan test suite yaz. if/else, for, while, exception handling dahil.",
    "starter_code": "def process_data(data, mode='strict'):\n    if not data:\n        return []\n    result = []\n    for item in data:\n        try:\n            if mode == 'strict':\n                if not isinstance(item, int):\n                    raise ValueError\n            result.append(item * 2)\n        except (ValueError, TypeError):\n            if mode == 'strict':\n                raise\n            result.append(None)\n    return result\n\ndef test_process_data_all_branches():\n    pass\n",
    "test_cases": [
      {
        "input": {
          "data": [
            1,
            2,
            3
          ],
          "mode": "strict"
        },
        "expected": [
          2,
          4,
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "data": [],
          "mode": "strict"
        },
        "expected": []
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "data": [
            1,
            "x",
            3
          ],
          "mode": "lenient"
        },
        "expected": [
          2,
          null,
          6
        ]
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "data": [
            1,
            "x"
          ],
          "mode": "strict"
        },
        "expected": "raises_ValueError"
      },
      {
        "input": {
          "data": [
            1,
            null,
            3
          ],
          "mode": "lenient"
        },
        "expected": [
          2,
          null,
          6
        ]
      }
    ],
    "hints": [
      "Branch coverage: if/else, for, except, return hepsi test edilmeli",
      "Edge cases: bos liste, tek eleman, buyuk liste",
      "Error path: invalid input -> exception test"
    ],
    "explanation": "Coverage-driven testing: fonksiyonun her branch'ini bir test ile kapsa. Branch coverage yuzde 100 hedef ama her zaman mumkun degil. Edge cases (bos, tek, max), error path (invalid input -> exception), ve happy path ayri testler.",
    "complexity": "O(n) per test",
    "related_concepts": [
      "coverage",
      "branch-coverage",
      "edge-cases",
      "TDD"
    ],
    "related_question_ids": [
      1115,
      1116,
      1117
    ],
    "tags": [
      "testing",
      "coverage",
      "intermediate",
      "testing"
    ],
    "tutorial_slug": null,
    "slug": "coverage-driven-test-suite",
    "_rendered_explanation": "Coverage-driven testing: fonksiyonun her branch'ini bir test ile kapsa. Branch coverage yuzde 100 hedef ama her zaman mumkun degil. Edge cases (bos, tek, max), error path (invalid input -> exception), ve happy path ayri testler. Production ortaminda bu fonksiyon icin defensive programming (input validation, type checks), comprehensive testing (unit + integration) ve performance profiling (cProfile ile) yapilmali. Edge caseler (bos input, None, buyuk degerler) production bug'larin yuzde seksenini olusturur. Pure function tercih edilirse test edilebilirlik artar, side effectler minimize edilir. Type hints ve docstring ile kod kalitesi yukselir."
