    "explanation": "Graph BFS en temel graph algoritmasıdır.\n\nfrom collections import deque\ndef bfs_graph(n, graph, start):\n    visited = {start}\n    queue = deque([start])\n    order = []\n    while queue:\n        node = queue.popleft()\n        order.append(node)\n        for neighbor in graph.get(node, []):\n            if neighbor not in visited:\n                visited.add(neighbor); queue.append(neighbor)\n    return order\n\nMülakat notu: Adjacency matrix vs list? Sparse graph = list (O(E) vs O(V²)). BFS shortest path (unweighted), connected components, bipartite check için kullanılır.",
