    "explanation": "Trie (prefix tree) string'leri O(L) zamanda arar (L = kelime uzunluğu).\n\nclass TrieNode:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.children = {}\n        self.is_end = False\n\nclass Trie:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.root = TrieNode()\n    def insert(self, word):\n        node = self.root\n        for char in word:\n            if char not in node.children:\n                node.children[char] = TrieNode()\n            node = node.children[char]\n        node.is_end = True\n    def search(self, word):\n        node = self.root\n        for char in word:\n            if char not in node.children: return False\n            node = node.children[char]\n        return node.is_end\n    def starts_with(self, prefix):\n        node = self.root\n        for char in prefix:\n            if char not in node.children: return False\n            node = node.children[char]\n        return True\n\nMülakat notu: Trie vs hash? Trie = prefix sorguları için O(L), hash O(L) tek kelime ama prefix için O(L*N). Trie bellek tradeoff: O(26*L) node vs Hash O(L).",
    "complexity": "O(L) insert/search/starts_with",
